---
title: Brown Sugar and Mustard-Glazed Salmon with Corn on the Cob and Wedge Salad
description: This summer feasts features succulent salmon with sweet and savoury glaze that couldn't be more Canadian. Corn on the cob and toasts are slathered with a rich chive compound butter. Kick it old school with a wedge salad, topped with DIY ranch, heirloom baby tomatoes and crispy shallots!
